## Answer (2)

The query answers your question exactly. I think that the question is worded to say "how many times has the Italian national soccer team won the world championships" and, to this end, not necessarily directed at Wikidata (which is where I would expect this information to be located, but which I didn't check first).

The query works in this manner:

- WD:Q18925: which tells is which team won (the query filters to just that).
